com.amazon.clouddrive.configuration

Interface EndpointsCache

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimpleEndpointsCache

    public interface EndpointsCache

    Defines a cache for holding the meta-data and content endpoints used for making requests to Amazon Cloud Drive. This cache should not be an indefinite cache, with entries recommended to be expired daily.
